data.description: UPGRADED 4 BEDROOM HOME IN DESIRABLE PECAN CREEK SOUTH. THIS BEAUTIFUL HOME IS SITUATED ON GREENBELT LOT AND HAS A CHARMING FRONT PORCH. UPGRADED INCLUDE A GOURMET KITCHEN WITH CHERRY CABINETS, STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, GAS COOKTOP AND 2 WALL OVENS. FAMILY ROOM HAS BLT-IN ENTERTAINMENT CTR AND STACKED STONE GAS FIREPLACE. CLOSE TO SCHOOLS AND SHOPPING. NEWLY BUILT BANNER HOSPITAL LESS THAN A MILE AWAY.
